data.description: Welcome to your dream home! This stunning 3-bedroom remodel, completed in 2020, boasts an open living room flowing seamlessly into a modern kitchen and dining area. Step outside to a screened-in patio and deck with a retractable awning, great for outdoor gatherings. Enjoy ample closet space, including an ensuite in the primary bedroom. With sleek finishes and practical features throughout, this home offers contemporary comfort and style in a serene neighborhood setting. Be sure to check out the awesome pantry that can be rolled out if access to HVAC system is needed.
